125
00:08:23,440 --> 00:08:25,240
Fine, we'll train another day.

126
00:08:27,080 --> 00:08:28,160
Take care, Master!

127
00:08:29,760 --> 00:08:31,320
[As long as I stay with Master,]

128
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:32,760
[I'll find a shot to sneak]

129
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:34,440
[into the dungeon and find Ningmeng!]

130
00:08:50,080 --> 00:08:50,640
Hongning,

131
00:08:51,280 --> 00:08:51,840
although you're not officially

132
