141
00:09:31,640 --> 00:09:33,400
[Just to catch one more glimpse of me,]

142
00:09:34,040 --> 00:09:35,440
[you're really willing to]

143
00:09:36,040 --> 00:09:37,880
[work day and night?]

144
00:09:42,120 --> 00:09:43,760
[Sweeping's the perfect excuse]

145
00:09:43,880 --> 00:09:45,160
[to go find Ningmeng in the dungeon!]

146
00:09:45,800 --> 00:09:46,840
[Oh, Hongning,]

147
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:48,880
[why didn't you think of this sooner?]

148
00:09:52,040 --> 00:09:52,640
[Could it really be]

149
00:09:53,560 --> 00:09:55,560
