151
00:10:13,280 --> 00:10:13,760
Hey, junior.

152
00:10:14,640 --> 00:10:15,480
Time to eat.

153
00:10:17,600 --> 00:10:18,640
Senior…

154
00:10:23,680 --> 00:10:24,200
Wait!

155
00:10:24,400 --> 00:10:25,960
You've been eating like a horse lately!

156
00:10:26,400 --> 00:10:27,520
I'm still growing, alright?

157
00:10:27,920 --> 00:10:29,000
You're huge already!

158
00:10:29,120 --> 00:10:30,280
No more to grow.

159
00:10:59,040 --> 00:10:59,560
Eat up.

160
00:11:01,720 --> 00:11:02,680
Your words

161
00:11:03,120 --> 00:11:04,560
