165
00:11:11,960 --> 00:11:13,680
Why are you so picky?

166
00:11:14,040 --> 00:11:15,400
I bring you food every day,

167
00:11:15,520 --> 00:11:16,760
and I've gotta be polite too?

168
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:20,040
Nice talk

169
00:11:20,440 --> 00:11:20,960
and I'll have a

170
00:11:21,080 --> 00:11:22,320
