171
00:11:22,600 --> 00:11:23,040
I…

172
00:11:27,520 --> 00:11:28,320
Fine.

173
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:30,440
Then…

174
00:11:31,640 --> 00:11:32,360
Miss,

175
00:11:33,520 --> 00:11:34,320
