179
00:12:07,200 --> 00:12:09,680
Thanks for looking after me these days.

180
00:12:10,280 --> 00:12:11,120
You helped me out,

181
00:12:12,480 --> 00:12:13,800
why not go all the way

182
00:12:14,280 --> 00:12:15,080
and let me leave?

183
00:12:18,520 --> 00:12:19,760
I won't let you off!

184
00:12:20,840 --> 00:12:21,440
You're keeping me…

185
00:12:24,920 --> 00:12:25,920
You're keeping me locked up here,

186
00:12:26,080 --> 00:12:26,920
what's the point?

187
00:12:27,600 --> 00:12:28,040
I…

188
00:12:29,280 --> 00:12:29,840
I…

189
00:12:31,720 --> 00:12:32,640
I just want you to eat more

190
00:12:32,800 --> 00:12:33,400
and put on some weight!

191
00:12:33,560 --> 00:12:34,280
So when I turn you in,

192
00:12:34,440 --> 00:12:34,960
they'll think

193
00:12:35,080 --> 00:12:36,400
I caught some big pixie!

194
00:12:36,600 --> 00:12:37,040
Why else

195
00:12:37,200 --> 00:12:38,160
would I treat you so nicely?

196
00:12:43,560 --> 00:12:44,520
Still the same!

197
00:12:44,640 --> 00:12:45,680
Not any change!

198
00:12:46,080 --> 00:12:46,720
Still such a pain,

199
00:12:46,840 --> 00:12:47,720
still so annoying!

200
