206
00:13:46,600 --> 00:13:47,440
Pity me?

207
00:13:48,480 --> 00:13:49,360
Didn't you see Master

208
00:13:49,640 --> 00:13:50,880
personally training Hongning?

209
00:13:51,880 --> 00:13:52,320
That's…

210
00:13:52,520 --> 00:13:54,040
'cause Master's scared Hongning's too slow

211
00:13:54,160 --> 00:13:55,760
