224
00:14:16,040 --> 00:14:17,760
Then what do foxes like?

225
00:14:19,920 --> 00:14:20,520
No clue.

226
00:14:21,720 --> 00:14:22,840
Why ask me?

227
00:14:23,040 --> 00:14:24,280
Go ask Senior Lujiu.

228
00:14:25,320 --> 00:14:26,120
Good point.

229
00:14:27,320 --> 00:14:28,360
No idea when he's

230
00:14:28,520 --> 00:14:29,520
