231
00:14:40,640 --> 00:14:41,160
Master,

232
00:14:42,320 --> 00:14:43,760
I lost Hongning.

233
00:14:45,200 --> 00:14:46,720
It's my fault, Master!

234
00:14:47,320 --> 00:14:48,680
All my fault!

235
00:14:49,600 --> 00:14:51,040
Master!

236
00:15:30,120 --> 00:15:31,160
Sir,

237
00:15:33,040 --> 00:15:34,480
can I have one last hug?

238
00:15:35,880 --> 00:15:36,840
I only came

239
00:15:38,120 --> 00:15:40,240
to congratulate you on your wedding

240
00:15:40,400 --> 00:15:41,680
with NCR Matriarch.

241
00:15:44,960 --> 00:15:45,880
Sir,

242
00:15:48,200 --> 00:15:50,080
I don't want to be your Empress anymore.

243
00:16:26,400 --> 00:16:27,080
[Hongning,]

244
00:16:29,280 --> 00:16:30,200
[in the last life,]

245
00:16:31,400 --> 00:16:32,880
[I broke my promise to you.]

246
00:16:34,600 --> 00:16:35,800
[Did fate bring us back]

247
00:16:36,840 --> 00:16:38,640
