252
00:17:07,440 --> 00:17:08,400
Keep training.

253
00:17:59,000 --> 00:17:59,640
Master,

254
00:18:00,280 --> 00:18:01,320
why is your trauma

255
00:18:01,760 --> 00:18:03,080
acting up again?

256
00:18:06,560 --> 00:18:07,280
It's fine.

257
00:18:08,240 --> 00:18:09,880
I'll be okay after some rest.

258
00:18:11,240 --> 00:18:11,880
Oh right, Master,

259
00:18:12,120 --> 00:18:12,960
