260
00:18:13,560 --> 00:18:15,360
Lately some of the disciples

261
00:18:15,960 --> 00:18:17,120
have been talking behind our backs.

262
00:18:17,560 --> 00:18:18,200
I know.

263
00:18:18,960 --> 00:18:20,280
Hongning isn't a formal disciple,

264
00:18:20,600 --> 00:18:21,560
and her foundation is weak.

265
00:18:22,320 --> 00:18:23,560
I've been

266
00:18:24,400 --> 00:18:25,800
too strict with her.

267
00:18:28,840 --> 00:18:29,400
Master,

268
00:18:30,000 --> 00:18:30,960
I mean…

269
00:18:31,640 --> 00:18:33,400
With some many disciples in the Academy,

270
00:18:34,080 --> 00:18:35,800
