282
00:18:59,880 --> 00:19:00,160
Come on!

283
00:19:00,320 --> 00:19:00,920
No need!

284
00:19:01,200 --> 00:19:02,080
It's okay really!

285
00:19:02,400 --> 00:19:02,920
I…

286
00:19:03,040 --> 00:19:04,560
I'm not cold, really!

287
00:19:13,440 --> 00:19:14,680
