00:19:31,160 --> 00:19:32,560
Never underestimate

295
00:19:32,720 --> 00:19:35,080
a constable's skills and instincts.

296
00:19:36,240 --> 00:19:37,440
Can I keep it?

297
00:19:37,600 --> 00:19:38,400
I get lost all the time.

298
00:19:39,120 --> 00:19:40,000
Sure thing!

299
00:19:41,080 --> 00:19:41,600
Thanks!

300
00:19:42,000 --> 00:19:42,680
No prob.

301
00:19:49,280 --> 00:19:52,560
Senior Bailing's pet corner.

302
00:19:53,240 --> 00:19:54,440
He keeps pets?

303
00:19:54,960 --> 00:19:56,280
Heard he's got a fox.

304
00:19:56,560 --> 00:19:57,160
Oh and

305
00:19:57,440 --> 00:19:59,200
don't tell anyone about this!

306
00:19:59,720 --> 00:20:01,000
It's his secret!

307
00:20:01,680 --> 00:20:02,600
I won't.

308
00:20:05,160 --> 00:20:05,760
Thanks!

309
00:20:08,720 --> 00:20:10,280
You sure know a lot.

310
00:20:11,480 --> 00:20:12,680
Told you,

311
00:20:12,920 --> 00:20:14,600
never doubt my ability.

312
00:20:20,720 --> 00:20:21,720
Since everyone

313
00:20:22,120 --> 00:20:24,040
thinks I treat Hongning differently,

314
00:20:25,280 --> 00:20:26,120
then maybe

315
00:20:27,680 --> 00:20:29,200
she should get her own room.

316
00:20:30,320 --> 00:20:31,800
Just to avoid disputes.

317
00:20:32,560 --> 00:20:34,040
Wenxin, go check

318
00:20:34,400 --> 00:20:35,760
if the new dorm's got enough blankets

319
00:20:35,920 --> 00:20:36,880
and firewood.

320
00:20:37,080 --> 00:20:38,640
If not, get more from the shed.

321
00:20:39,440 --> 00:20:40,280
I'm off the grid for a bit.

322
00:20:41,440 --> 00:20:41,960
This is…

323
00:20:46,240 --> 00:20:47,000
Hongning,

324
00:20:48,440 --> 00:20:52,400
I think Master really cares about you.

325
00:20:53,520 --> 00:20:54,240
Does he?

326
00:20:55,240 --> 00:20:56,400
The other seniors said

327
00:20:56,600 --> 00:20:58,720
Master never teaches anyone personally.

328
00:20:59,040 --> 00:21:00,600
But with you, he does…

329
00:21:01,480 --> 00:21:04,080
That's because he's always
off the grid cultivating,

330
00:21:04,520 --> 00:21:07,640
and he worries I'd slow Cangwu down.

331
00:21:08,680 --> 00:21:10,200
Is that true?

332
00:21:10,520 --> 00:21:11,160
Isn't it?

333
00:21:12,480 --> 00:21:13,520
If someone

334
00:21:14,000 --> 00:21:15,720
really cared about you,

335
00:21:16,000 --> 00:21:16,520
how could he not notice

336
00:21:16,640 --> 00:21:18,040
if you're eating right

337
00:21:18,200 --> 00:21:18,840
or sleeping okay,

338
00:21:19,120 --> 00:21:20,320
only pushing you on school stuff?

339
00:21:20,480 --> 00:21:21,240
Anyway,

340
00:21:21,760 --> 00:21:23,080
I just wanna

341
00:21:23,720 --> 00:21:26,560
hog this big bed all to myself,

342
00:21:26,720 --> 00:21:28,040
so comfy!

343
00:21:28,920 --> 00:21:29,840
Dream on!

344
00:21:33,320 --> 00:21:33,960
Hongning.

345
00:21:36,880 --> 00:21:38,240
Senior Bailing, what are you doing here?

346
00:21:39,040 --> 00:21:39,760
Master says

347
00:21:40,120 --> 00:21:41,440
this room's too small for Hongning,

348
00:21:41,800 --> 00:21:43,240
and "he" is moving to the new dorms.

349
00:21:45,160 --> 00:21:46,720
[Not much time left for you!]

350
00:21:46,920 --> 00:21:47,840
Message delivered,

351
00:21:48,000 --> 00:21:48,760
go or don't, I don't care

352
00:21:49,120 --> 00:21:49,960
I'm going!

353
00:21:50,120 --> 00:21:50,560
Now!

354
00:21:53,200 --> 00:21:54,520
So we're not cuddling anymore?

355
00:22:00,120 --> 00:22:02,320
Why is this fox so dramatic?

356
00:22:06,320 --> 00:22:08,040
What if she doesn't eat?

357
00:22:29,520 --> 00:22:30,000
What now?

358
00:22:47,200 --> 00:22:48,000
Bailing…

359
00:22:48,720 --> 00:22:51,160
[will he ever learn to lock a door?]

360
00:23:29,920 --> 00:23:32,000
Great, now we're both stuck.

361
00:23:33,400 --> 00:23:34,400
If you hadn't dragged me here,

362
00:23:34,720 --> 00:23:35,640
this wouldn't have happened!

363
00:23:37,360 --> 00:23:38,840
Why is everything I do wrong?

364
00:23:39,280 --> 00:23:40,480
You and Master are both impossible!

365
00:23:49,000 --> 00:23:49,440
Forget it.

366
00:23:52,000 --> 00:23:52,640
Go ahead and eat.

367
00:23:53,960 --> 00:23:54,400
Not hungry.

368
00:23:57,000 --> 00:23:58,640
I really don't get you!

369
00:23:59,320 --> 00:24:01,960
Why are you always so hard on yourself?

370
00:24:02,720 --> 00:24:03,640
You're starving,

371
00:24:03,920 --> 00:24:05,240
but still acting all proud!

372
00:24:05,400 --> 00:24:06,880
Your hand's badly hurt,

373
00:24:07,480 --> 00:24:08,440
but all you think about is picking

374
00:24:08,760 --> 00:24:10,560
fights with those heavenly soldiers!

375
00:24:11,240 --> 00:24:11,800
What?

376
00:24:12,360 --> 00:24:14,200
Do you hate comfort?

377
00:24:16,400 --> 00:24:17,760
Life's not always comfy!

378
00:24:18,360 --> 00:24:19,640
When duty calls,

379
00:24:20,000 --> 00:24:21,040
comfort means nothing!

380
00:24:23,520 --> 00:24:24,480
Who says that?

381
00:24:25,400 --> 00:24:26,040
First of all,

382
00:24:26,880 --> 00:24:28,520
to be yourself,

383
00:24:28,920 --> 00:24:30,760
you've got to love yourself.

384
00:24:31,680 --> 00:24:33,560
Only then can you handle

385
00:24:33,880 --> 00:24:35,320
real duty and responsibility.

386
00:24:36,760 --> 00:24:38,320
Also being comfy

387
00:24:38,680 --> 00:24:40,920
doesn't mean being spoiled.

388
00:24:41,880 --> 00:24:43,840
It means listening to your heart,

389
00:24:44,320 --> 00:24:46,320
that's how you find peace.

390
00:24:50,520 --> 00:24:51,760
If I hadn't heard it myself, I'd

391
00:24:52,160 --> 00:24:53,800
never believe those words came from you.

392
00:24:57,400 --> 00:24:58,080
Well…

393
00:24:58,320 --> 00:25:00,120
I've got loads of charm!

394
00:25:00,920 --> 00:25:02,520
Take your time to feel it out.

395
00:25:07,200 --> 00:25:08,120
Why are you still standing there?

396
00:25:08,440 --> 00:25:09,200
Go and have your meal!

397
00:25:10,480 --> 00:25:11,160
Meal?

398
00:25:11,600 --> 00:25:12,920
You mean your spirit power or the rabbit?

399
00:25:17,800 --> 00:25:18,600
I'm an immortal,

400
00:25:18,760 --> 00:25:19,480
and you're a pixie, how can you

401
00:25:20,000 --> 00:25:21,600
gave away spirit power like snacks?

402
00:25:23,640 --> 00:25:25,080
Because I want to. Problem?

403
00:25:29,880 --> 00:25:30,320
Here.

404
00:25:34,960 --> 00:25:35,760
Take it back!

405
00:25:40,440 --> 00:25:41,000
Later,

406
00:25:41,560 --> 00:25:42,880
when I truly need it,

407
00:25:44,360 --> 00:25:45,080
you can give it back.

408
00:25:55,800 --> 00:25:56,320
Deal!

409
00:26:27,720 --> 00:26:28,800
When awake,

410
00:26:30,000 --> 00:26:31,080
you chatter nonstop.

411
00:26:33,000 --> 00:26:34,360
Being quiet like this

412
00:26:36,360 --> 00:26:37,440
isn't so bad.

413
00:26:59,680 --> 00:27:00,600
Upon closer look...

414
00:27:02,120 --> 00:27:03,040
you're not unattractive.

415
00:27:33,080 --> 00:27:34,800
Why haven't seen Master today?

416
00:27:35,400 --> 00:27:37,560
I heard he's gone off-grid for recuperation.

417
00:27:37,760 --> 00:27:39,320
He won't emerge for some time.

418
00:27:39,680 --> 00:27:40,640
Recuperation?

419
00:27:41,240 --> 00:27:43,080
People say he suffered grave injuries.

420
00:27:43,560 --> 00:27:45,280
The cause remains unclear.

421
00:27:45,720 --> 00:27:46,400
The only one who knows

422
00:27:46,600 --> 00:27:47,720
is Brother Lujiu

423
00:27:47,880 --> 00:27:48,640
He's a fox pixie

424
00:27:48,800 --> 00:27:49,880
who's followed

425
00:27:50,040 --> 00:27:51,640
Master loyally.

426
00:27:52,160 --> 00:27:52,560
Then why

427
00:27:52,680 --> 00:27:54,520
have I never seen Brother Lujiu?

428
00:27:55,080 --> 00:27:55,880
They say

429
00:27:56,040 --> 00:27:57,000
Master dispatched him

430
00:27:57,200 --> 00:27:59,800
on some secret mission

431
00:27:59,960 --> 00:28:01,240
that's still ongoing.

432
00:28:04,320 --> 00:28:05,040
I'll head out now.

433
00:28:12,120 --> 00:28:13,360
Fo... Brother Lujiu?

434
00:28:13,960 --> 00:28:14,520
You're back!

435
00:28:14,720 --> 00:28:15,320
You're back!

436
00:28:16,400 --> 00:28:18,720
If I catch you slacking off again,

437
00:28:19,200 --> 00:28:21,120
I'll toss you into the alchemy furnace!

438
00:28:22,040 --> 00:28:23,080
Do you realize

439
00:28:23,280 --> 00:28:24,120
slacking on duties

440
00:28:24,240 --> 00:28:25,960
might cause mistakes!

441
00:28:32,880 --> 00:28:33,320
Come on!

442
00:28:33,480 --> 00:28:34,360
Come on! Hurry!

443
00:28:38,040 --> 00:28:38,960
Brother Lujiu.

444
00:28:42,240 --> 00:28:43,120
He's Lujiu?

445
00:28:43,920 --> 00:28:45,160
What are they doing?

446
00:28:45,360 --> 00:28:46,040
Such a commotion.

447
00:28:46,080 --> 00:28:46,880
Utterly ruleless!

448
00:28:53,000 --> 00:28:53,840
Brother Lujiu.

449
00:28:59,960 --> 00:29:00,600
This is

450
00:29:00,760 --> 00:29:02,880
the world's most potent poison

451
00:29:03,040 --> 00:29:04,800
I've researched for ages.

452
00:29:05,960 --> 00:29:07,960
The only one of its kind in the realm.

453
00:29:08,320 --> 00:29:10,280
Whoever encounters it faces doom.

454
00:29:11,040 --> 00:29:11,400
-Wanna have a...
-Brother Lujiu.

455
00:29:11,400 --> 00:29:12,200
Brother Lujiu.

456
00:29:12,480 --> 00:29:13,040
No, no, no thanks!

457
00:29:18,120 --> 00:29:18,920
Brother Lujiu

458
00:29:19,080 --> 00:29:19,720
Greetings, Brother Lujiu!

459
00:29:31,400 --> 00:29:32,160
Lujiu is back?

460
00:29:48,240 --> 00:29:49,640
Brother Lujiu?

461
00:29:51,880 --> 00:29:52,760
Brother Lujiu,

462
00:29:53,320 --> 00:29:54,080
what's wrong?

463
00:29:54,240 --> 00:29:55,240
Kneeling in penance again?

464
00:29:57,360 --> 00:29:58,320
Actually, I came to

465
00:29:58,480 --> 00:30:00,040
ask you something.

466
00:30:00,440 --> 00:30:01,360
Since you're also a fox—

467
00:30:01,880 --> 00:30:02,720
besides rabbits,

468
00:30:03,000 --> 00:30:04,120
what's your usual diet?

469
00:30:04,800 --> 00:30:05,400
Owls?

470
00:30:05,960 --> 00:30:07,000
Or rats?

471
00:30:08,080 --> 00:30:08,800
Scram.

472
00:30:10,520 --> 00:30:11,360
Then tell me

473
00:30:11,560 --> 00:30:13,000
your hobbies.

474
00:30:13,400 --> 00:30:14,200
Like

475
00:30:14,400 --> 00:30:15,000
tree-climbing?

476
00:30:15,360 --> 00:30:15,920
Burrow-digging?

477
00:30:16,280 --> 00:30:17,880
Or maybe mud-rolling?

478
00:30:19,120 --> 00:30:22,800
Get lost!

479
00:30:25,800 --> 00:30:26,240
Still that fiery temper

480
00:30:26,320 --> 00:30:27,240
after all these years!

481
00:30:28,360 --> 00:30:29,160
One more thing—

482
00:30:29,480 --> 00:30:30,000
I took

483
00:30:30,160 --> 00:30:31,880
your goose-down quilt

484
00:30:32,120 --> 00:30:33,040
in your room to Hongning

485
00:30:33,200 --> 00:30:34,360
per Master's order.

486
00:30:34,520 --> 00:30:35,680
Not stolen!

487
00:30:36,080 --> 00:30:36,960
Though I can't fathom

488
00:30:37,040 --> 00:30:38,240
what madness drives

489
00:30:38,320 --> 00:30:39,120
Master's favoritism.

490
00:30:40,600 --> 00:30:41,640
Whatever! It doesn't matter!

491
00:30:41,800 --> 00:30:42,880
I'm going to Master now.

492
00:30:43,400 --> 00:30:44,240
Persevere!

493
00:30:45,480 --> 00:30:45,960
Persevere!

494
00:30:53,200 --> 00:30:53,880
Hongning?

495
00:30:59,640 --> 00:31:00,720
Hongning!

496
00:31:07,880 --> 00:31:08,520
Master, are you inside?

497
00:31:09,240 --> 00:31:10,160
Master! Master! Master!

498
00:31:10,400 --> 00:31:10,880
Enter.

499
00:31:20,080 --> 00:31:20,760
Master,

500
00:31:22,200 --> 00:31:22,840
you're in seclusion?

501
00:31:24,240 --> 00:31:25,040
What do you think?

502
00:31:27,280 --> 00:31:27,840
Well,

503
00:31:28,600 --> 00:31:30,120
I have something to report.

504
00:31:30,280 --> 00:31:31,360
Prepared to explain

505
00:31:31,520 --> 00:31:33,200
your quintessence loss?

506
00:31:34,800 --> 00:31:36,600
You already know what I'd say?

507
00:31:40,320 --> 00:31:41,080
Let me clarify!

508
00:31:41,400 --> 00:31:42,920
Here's what happened:

509
00:31:43,480 --> 00:31:44,760
Down the mountain,

510
00:31:45,160 --> 00:31:45,840
I encountered

511
00:31:46,000 --> 00:31:47,800
a 10,000-year-old herb pixie.

512
00:31:48,360 --> 00:31:50,480
She disguised as a food vendor.

513
00:31:50,640 --> 00:31:52,040
I initially didn't recognize it!

514
00:31:53,080 --> 00:31:53,680
Taking pity,

515
00:31:53,880 --> 00:31:55,760
I bought medicinal soup.

516
00:31:56,200 --> 00:31:57,000
Who'd imagine

517
00:31:57,200 --> 00:31:59,320
lethal poison within!

518
00:32:00,680 --> 00:32:02,520
Thus I lost 200 years' quintessence.

519
00:32:02,840 --> 00:32:03,480
Then I

520
00:32:03,640 --> 00:32:05,760
battled her for three days!

521
00:32:07,000 --> 00:32:07,920
That's the truth.

522
00:32:09,720 --> 00:32:10,960
What did the herb pixie look like?

523
00:32:13,240 --> 00:32:14,360
The herb pixie...

524
00:32:15,600 --> 00:32:16,880
Well, the herb pixie...

525
00:32:17,160 --> 00:32:18,160
When she revealed

526
00:32:18,720 --> 00:32:19,840
her true form,

527
00:32:20,040 --> 00:32:21,560
she was over six feet tall

528
00:32:22,040 --> 00:32:23,280
with massive wings,

529
00:32:23,960 --> 00:32:24,840
glowing eyes,

530
00:32:25,880 --> 00:32:28,000
and a body burly as a black bear!

531
00:32:29,840 --> 00:32:31,320
Didn't you claim being dragged

532
00:32:31,960 --> 00:32:33,400
into forced marriage that day?

533
00:32:37,240 --> 00:32:37,800
Yes!

534
00:32:38,400 --> 00:32:40,640
The village chief...

535
00:32:41,320 --> 00:32:42,160
he was...

536
00:32:42,320 --> 00:32:42,760
Enough.

537
00:32:43,720 --> 00:32:44,440
Drop the act.

538
00:32:45,480 --> 00:32:46,080
Speak truth.

539
00:32:47,680 --> 00:32:48,280
Master,

540
00:32:48,640 --> 00:32:49,920
I'll be frank.

541
00:32:50,400 --> 00:32:52,800
A lone white hare darts east and west,

542
00:32:53,120 --> 00:32:54,200
glancing back in unrest.

543
00:32:54,680 --> 00:32:55,800
New clothes may shine brighter,

544
00:32:56,120 --> 00:32:56,400
but old...

545
00:32:56,560 --> 00:32:57,720
Close the door behind you.

546
00:32:59,680 --> 00:33:00,280
Master,

547
00:33:00,880 --> 00:33:02,600
I just wanted to say—

548
00:33:04,360 --> 00:33:06,800
you dote so on that new disciple,

549
00:33:07,200 --> 00:33:09,560
could you spare me some kindness?

550
00:33:12,480 --> 00:33:12,960
Out with it.

551
00:33:13,560 --> 00:33:15,680
More martial manuals?

552
00:33:18,360 --> 00:33:21,720
Actually, I just need some money.

553
00:33:24,680 --> 00:33:25,600
Why do you start craving money

554
00:33:25,760 --> 00:33:26,960
after descending the mountain?

555
00:33:27,840 --> 00:33:28,560
Master,

556
00:33:29,280 --> 00:33:30,720
didn't you always

557
00:33:32,280 --> 00:33:33,160
teach us that

558
00:33:33,560 --> 00:33:35,400
cultivation requires

559
00:33:36,480 --> 00:33:38,960
worldly experience first?

560
00:33:39,960 --> 00:33:40,840
By mortal standards,

561
00:33:41,120 --> 00:33:42,040
you've reached

562
00:33:42,360 --> 00:33:43,880
coming-of-age.

563
00:33:44,440 --> 00:33:45,960
You should make your own money.

564
00:33:46,160 --> 00:33:47,040
But Cangwu Academy

565
00:33:47,200 --> 00:33:48,960
never taught me how to do that.

566
00:33:49,280 --> 00:33:50,160
How did Master Wenxin

567
00:33:50,280 --> 00:33:51,520
teach you Qi cultivation?

568
00:33:53,800 --> 00:33:54,280
Enlightenment.

569
00:34:07,880 --> 00:34:08,520
[Why is it so tough]

570
00:34:08,719 --> 00:34:09,679
[to get some money]

571
00:34:09,679 --> 00:34:11,320
[to make the little fox happy?]

572
00:34:18,120 --> 00:34:18,760
Why did you

573
00:34:19,320 --> 00:34:20,159
come here?

574
00:34:20,440 --> 00:34:21,440
I… Why…

575
00:34:21,639 --> 00:34:22,320
Why? Why?

576
00:34:22,639 --> 00:34:23,600
What is your purpose?

577
00:34:24,199 --> 00:34:25,679
Wh-what purpose?

578
00:34:26,600 --> 00:34:28,400
How did you evade my surveillance?

579
00:34:28,880 --> 00:34:30,320
Evade you?

580
00:34:30,760 --> 00:34:31,239
No!

581
00:34:31,719 --> 00:34:32,520
Don't explain.

582
00:34:33,199 --> 00:34:33,960
I don't want to know.

583
00:34:34,440 --> 00:34:35,239
No excuses.

584
00:34:37,600 --> 00:34:38,520
You… you…

585
00:34:38,719 --> 00:34:39,760
You know me?

586
00:34:41,080 --> 00:34:41,639
I...

587
00:34:41,840 --> 00:34:42,560
I don't know you!

588
00:34:42,920 --> 00:34:43,719
We never met!

589
00:34:44,040 --> 00:34:44,560
Then…

590
00:34:47,920 --> 00:34:48,600
I failed...

591
00:34:49,800 --> 00:34:50,960
to contain you.

592
00:34:54,960 --> 00:34:55,560
